column5: Nice pictorial, that is hardcore fishing conditions. The brown really makes it all good.
wow, good on ya for getting out there.  Beauty fish!
Whoa! Those are some serious conditions out there bro!! Must've been FREEZING! Hahaha...
Love the pictures, nice catch there...looks like scary water there  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
Nice work man.  I think it's about time to put the ice gear aside for a weekend and cure my pin-itch as well.
Great pics....nasty conditions....good for you on getting out!

thanks guys, ive always wanted to be down there on a crazy snow storm. I remember seeing waynes big steelie pic from down there in a snow storm and that was always something i wanted to experience, no crazy huge bow though haha.  @Rob haha it was that cold bud, the first couple hours it was snowing hard but jsut falling straight down so it was nice then the wind picked up and thats when we packed it up. crappies soon =)
